Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:39.70,Typewriter Text Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(93,837.7)}Năng\N lực:\N Dạ \NXoa\N Bạch\N Tuyết
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:01.97,Default,Sign 1037,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
